WEBVTT

00:06:57.746 --> 00:07:02.748
And when the audience arrived to see
Adele's first live concert in five years,

00:07:02.772 --> 00:07:05.755
they were met with this image
of her eyes asleep.

00:07:06.964 --> 00:07:08.764
If they listened carefully,

00:07:08.788 --> 00:07:12.819
they would hear her sleeping breath
echoing around the arena,

00:07:12.843 --> 00:07:14.888
waiting to wake up.

00:07:14.912 --> 00:07:16.172
Here's how the show began.

00:07:16.775 --> 00:07:22.291
(Video: Cheers, applause)

00:07:22.315 --> 00:07:23.316
(Music)

00:07:23.340 --> 00:07:24.617
Adele: Hello.

00:07:24.641 --> 00:07:31.373
(Cheers, applause)